title: Boca das Torrinhas
body: It separates the Serra da Boaventura from the Serra do Curral das Freiras. The Sedum farinosum, a plant from the Crassulaceae family, and the Isoplexis Sceptrum, a shrub from the Scrophulariaceae family, are common in Boca das Torrinhas and its surroundings. See Torrinhas (Boca das).
